'''尼尔马拉·西塔拉曼'''（'''Nirmala Sitharaman'''，{{bd|1959年|8月18日|||catIdx=S}}）是一位[[印度|印度]]政治人物，现任印度财政和公司事务部长。自2014年起，她一直是[[印度议会|印度议会]]上议院[[联邦院_(印度)|联邦院]]的议员。西塔拉曼曾任印度国防部长，是继[[英迪拉·甘地|英迪拉·甘地]]之后第二位女性国防部长，第二位女财政部长，以及第一位全职女财政部长。她曾担任财政部下属的财政和公司事务国务部长和独立负责的工商部部长。在此之前，她曾担任[[印度人民党|印度人民党]]（BJP）的全国发言人。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.deccanchronicle.com/140604/nation-politics/article/bjp-leader-nirmala-sitharaman-gets-njr-rajya-sabha-seat|title=Deccan Chronicle: BJP leader Nirmala Sitharaman gets NJR Rajya Sabha seat|date=2014-06-04|access-date=2017-09-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170904030305/http://www.deccanchronicle.com/140604/nation-politics/article/bjp-leader-nirmala-sitharaman-gets-njr-rajya-sabha-seat#|archive-date=2017-09-04}}</ref>

==早年生活==
尼尔马拉·西塔拉曼出生于[[泰米尔纳德邦|泰米尔纳德邦]][[马杜赖|马杜赖]]的一个[[泰米尔语|泰米尔]]家庭。<ref>{{cite news|title=A power couple whom AP looks up to|url=https://www.timesofindia.com/city/hyderabad/A-power-couple-whom-AP-looks-up-to/articleshow/38766320.cms|publisher=Times of India|accessdate=2014-07-21}}</ref>她在[[金奈|金奈]]和[[蒂魯吉拉帕利|蒂魯吉拉帕利]]上学。<ref name=bst>{{cite news|last1=Phadnis|first1=Aditi|title=The rise and rise of Nirmala Sitharaman: From spokesperson to defence minister|url=http://www.business-standard.com/article/politics/rise-of-nirmala-sitharaman-from-spokesperson-to-defence-minister-117090400030_1.html|work={{tsl|en|Business Standard||Business Standard}}|date=2017-09-04|accessdate=2017-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170906121736/http://www.business-standard.com/article/politics/rise-of-nirmala-sitharaman-from-spokesperson-to-defence-minister-117090400030_1.html#|archive-date=2017-09-06}}</ref>她于1980年在{{tsl|en|Seethalakshmi Ramaswami College||Seethalakshmi Ramaswami学院}}获得经济学[[文學碩士|硕士]]学位，1984年在[[賈瓦哈拉爾·尼赫魯大學|賈瓦哈拉爾·尼赫魯大學]]获得经济学[[研究碩士|研究碩士]]学位。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Tiruchirapalli/nirmala-sitharaman-the-pride-of-tiruchi/article19618658.ece|title=Nirmala Sitharaman, the pride of Tiruchi|last=Krishnamoorthy|first=R.|date=2017-09-04|work=The Hindu|access-date=2019-06-02|issn=0971-751X|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171202124119/http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Tiruchirapalli/nirmala-sitharaman-the-pride-of-tiruchi/article19618658.ece|archive-date=2017-12-02}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://docs.myneta.info/affidavits/rajsab09aff/631/Nirmala%20Sitharaman.pdf|title=Rajya Sabha Affidavits|last=Sitharaman|first=Nirmala|date=2016-05-30|page=7|access-date=2020-07-15|archive-date=2022-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220422141053/http://docs.myneta.info/affidavits/rajsab09aff/631/Nirmala%20Sitharaman.pdf}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Nirmala Sitharaman appointed Finance Minister in Modi govt 2.0 as Arun Jaitley retreats |url=https://www.financialexpress.com/economy/nirmala-sitharaman-appointed-finance-minister-in-modi-govt-2-0-as-arun-jaitley-retreats/1594251/ |work=The Financial Express |date=2019-05-31 |access-date=2019-06-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190601011218/https://www.financialexpress.com/economy/nirmala-sitharaman-appointed-finance-minister-in-modi-govt-2-0-as-arun-jaitley-retreats/1594251/ |archive-date=2019-06-01  }}</ref>然后，她报名攻读经济学[[哲學博士|博士]]学位，重点研究印欧贸易，但是她的丈夫在[[倫敦政治經濟學院|倫敦政治經濟學院]]获得奖学金后搬到伦敦，使她无法完成学位。<ref name ="bs-sep2017">{{cite news |last1=Phadnis |first1=Aditi |title=The rise and rise of Nirmala Sitharaman: From spokesperson to defence minister |url=https://www.business-standard.com/article/politics/rise-of-nirmala-sitharaman-from-spokesperson-to-defence-minister-117090400030_1.html |work=Business Standard |date=2017-09-04 |access-date=2019-01-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190209220341/https://www.business-standard.com/article/politics/rise-of-nirmala-sitharaman-from-spokesperson-to-defence-minister-117090400030_1.html |archive-date=2019-02-09  }}</ref>

==政治生涯==
西塔拉曼于2006年加入[[印度人民党|印度人民党]]，并于2010年被任命为该党的发言人。2014年，她以初级[[部長|部長]]的身份加入[[纳伦德拉·莫迪|纳伦德拉·莫迪]]内阁，2014年6月当选为[[安得拉邦|安得拉邦]]的联邦院议员。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.thehindu.com/news/national/nirmala-elected-to-rajya-sabha/article6152636.ece|title=Nirmala elected to Rajya Sabha|date=2014-06-27|work=The Hindu|access-date=2019-01-07|others=Special Correspondent|issn=0971-751X|archive-date=2020-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200812153452/https://www.thehindu.com/news/national/nirmala-elected-to-rajya-sabha/article6152636.ece}}</ref><ref name=":0" />

2016年5月，她是[[印度人民党|印度人民党]]提名的12名候选人之一，参加于2016年6月11日举行的[[联邦院_(印度)|联邦院]]选举。她成功地赢得了[[卡纳塔克邦|卡纳塔克邦]]的席位。<ref>{{cite news|title=Naidu, Naqvi, Goyal among 12 in BJP's RS list|url=http://www.abplive.in/india-news/naidu-naqvi-goyal-among-12-in-bjps-rs-list-352440|accessdate=2016-05-30|publisher=ABP Live|date=2016-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160530152104/http://www.abplive.in/india-news/naidu-naqvi-goyal-among-12-in-bjps-rs-list-352440#|archive-date=2016-05-30}}</ref>

