o be formed; no decision on relief package|date=2020-03-20|website=Business Today|access-date=2020-03-20|archive-date=2020-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200519200151/https://www.businesstoday.in/current/economy-politics/coronavirus-impact-fm-led-economic-task-force-takes-stock-of-key-ministries/story/398804.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/business/india-business/government-forms-covid-19-economic-response-task-force-pm-modi/articleshow/74716284.cms|title=Covid 19 Economic Task Force: Government forms Covid-19 economic response task force, says PM Modi|date=2020-03-19|website=The Times of India|access-date=2020-03-20|archive-date=2020-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200507052311/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/business/india-business/government-forms-covid-19-economic-response-task-force-pm-modi/articleshow/74716284.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>

